view.name: Use Of Medical Imaging Measures
view.description: A list of hospitals and the corresponding Use of Medical Imaging ratings. These measures give you information about hospitals' use of medical imaging tests for outpatients. Medical Imaging are Tests that create images of various parts of the body to screen for or diagnose medical conditions. Examples of medical imaging include CT Scans, MRIs, and mammograms.
